### Obtener todos los pagos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments

### Obtener un pago por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/pay-123

### Obtener pago por reserva
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/reservation/res-123

### Crear un pago
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "res-123",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "transactionReference": "TXN-2025-001"
}

### Listar pagos por estado
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/status/PENDING

### Procesar un pago
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/payments/pay-123/process

### Completar un pago
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/payments/pay-123/complete

### Fallar un pago
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/payments/pay-123/fail?reason=Tarjeta%20rechazada

### Reembolsar un pago
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/payments/pay-123/refund

### Obtener total de pagos completados
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/stats/total-completed

### Obtener estad√≠sticas de pagos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/stats/count-by-status